title: ART by Bad Religion
description:
This is a fairly comprehensive collections of rarities by Bad Religion from the beginning of their career until about the mid- to late-nineties with a spiffy HTML menu, put together by the previous webmaster for thebrpage.net, I believe.

I couldn't find a torrent on the internet anywhere, but I did manage to find the CD I thought I had lost, so here it is.  Please download, seed, and share!
